nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.implSAT

Class SAT_SynthesisEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.implSAT.SAT_SynthesisEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SynthesisEngine

    public class SAT_SynthesisEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements SynthesisEngine
    The SAT_SynthesisEngine class represents a synthesis instance, i.e. it is represented with the set of inputs (tools, types, constraints and workflow lenght that is being explored).
    It is used to execute synthesis algorithm over the given input, implemented using MiniSAT solver.

    The class implements general synthesis interface SynthesisEngine.
    Author:
    Vedran Kasalica
